OL,7,FExposure to air pollution has been
OL,8,Flinked to a higher use of psychiatric
OL,9,Fservices in people with dementia, a
OL,10,Fstudy has shown.
OL,12,FThe research, led by academics at the
OL,13,FInstitute of Psychiatry, Psychology
OL,14,Fand Neuroscience at King's College
OL,15,FLondon, analysed data from 5,024
OL,16,Fpeople who have had dementia for nine
OL,17,Fyears, using detailed air-quality
OL,18,Fmodelling to estimate air pollution
OL,19,Flevels at their addresses in
OL,20,FSouthwark, Lambeth, Lewisham and
OL,21,FCroydon.
OL,3,CAir pollution linked to higher use of
OL,4,Cpsychiatric services in dementia
OL,5,Cpatients
